Roadmap

The Say Network project team has an initial focus on an MVP release approximately three months after launch. While the size of the community will determine the set of features delivered for MVP, the minimum set of features includes a familiar social media engagement experience integrated with the Say Network layer-1 to track activity related to SAC calculations.

Future use cases are constantly being explored and considered. The Say Network project is excited to build out working relationships with the user community and broader developer ecosystem in the web3 space.
